  "description": "A breathtaking night view of a cityscape illuminated with vibrant lights and a spectacular firework display. A long bridge with illuminated railings stretches across dark water, leading towards a densely populated city skyline. The fireworks explode in a burst of red, white, and blue above the bridge, creating a stunning visual contrast. The city buildings are lit up with golden and white lights, and a second bridge can be seen in the distance. The scene is dominated by a dark, shadowy background of trees and hills.",
